snippet.title: Slemmings VR - Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Slemmings VR is a game made during the VR-course at the Game Programming-program, at Yrgo (vocational university of Gothenburg)

Download the game here:
https://yrgo-game-programmer.itch.io/slemmings

Check the other games made by Yrgo Students over here:
https://yrgo-game-programmer.itch.io/


Credits:
Programming:
Niklas Lingsell
Pablo Sorribes Bernhard
Rikard Andersson
Simon Holmlund
Leroy Cortnex

Audio:
Pablo Sorribes Bernhard
Anders Hofsten
Therese Larsson

Graphics, UI & UX
Daniel Ygrelius
Peter Ihm
Emil Gradén

Special Thanks:
Robert Esbjörnsson
Richard (Lärarn)
Filip Andersson (aka fillefilip8)
